    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="letter">
                <pb n="1" facs="Edgeworth_NLS_42180_unknown_01_page01.jpg"/>
                <p>
                    Will you be so good to forward the<lb/>
                    enclosed packet to<lb/>
                    Mess<hi rend="superscript">rs</hi> <unclear><persName ref="./Personography.xml#CradC1">Cradock</persName></unclear> &amp; <persName ref="./Personography.xml#BaldR1">Baldwin</persName><lb/>
                </p>
                <p>
                    I have just looked at a copy we<lb/>
                    have of <title ref="./Workography.xml#Garry1"><choice><orig>Garryowen</orig><reg>Garry Owen</reg></choice></title> in the<lb/>
                    Christmas box and I see that<lb/>
                    there are in that very good<lb/>
                    <hi rend="underline">line engravings</hi> suited to the<lb/>
                    subject - <hi rend="underline">Wood cuts</hi> they<lb/>
                    may be for aught I know<lb/>
                </p>
             </div>
        </body>
